@startuml
' ============================================================
' Diagram   : Dynamic Failure Detection and Recovery - Policy Loop
' Section   : 14.10 Dynamic Failure Detection and Recovery
' Type      : Activity diagram
' Message   : The intelligent watchdog monitor and resilient
'             watchdog system perform sequential, policy-driven
'             recovery, escalating only when automatic recovery
'             attempts fail.
' ============================================================

title 14.10 Dynamic Failure Detection and Recovery\nSequential Recovery Policy

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Helvetica
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam roundCorner 6
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #F0F4F8
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #4A6B8A
skinparam ActivityDiamondBackgroundColor #FFF8DC
skinparam ActivityDiamondBorderColor #4A6B8A
skinparam PartitionBackgroundColor #FAFCFD
skinparam PartitionBorderColor #4A6B8A
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFF8DC
skinparam noteBorderColor #999999

|Intelligent Watchdog Monitor|
start
:1. Watch IT resources\n(track cloud consumer requests);

if (2. Failure detected?) then (no)
  :Continue watching;
  stop
else (yes)
endif

:3. Decide upon event\n(consult sequential recovery policy);

|Resilient Watchdog System|
:Step 1 - Restart the service;
if (Service restored?) then (yes)
  :4. Report;
  stop
else (no)
endif

:Step 2 - Restart Services X, Y\nthen restart the service;
if (Service restored?) then (yes)
  :Report;
  stop
else (no)
endif

:Step 3 - Stop services,\nclean temp folder,\nrestart the service;
if (Service restored?) then (yes)
  :Report;
  stop
else (no)
endif

:Step 4 - Escalate the problem;
note right
  Escalation actions include:
  running a batch file,
  console message, text message,
  email message, SNMP trap,
  ticket logging.
  ----
  Five core functions: watching,
  deciding, acting, reporting, escalating.
  Mechanisms: audit monitor, failover system,
  SLA management system, SLA monitor.
end note
:Notify operators;
stop

@enduml
